,{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 59:1","book":"Isa","chapter":59,"verse":1,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" Yet you are among us, "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 29:45","book":"Exo","chapter":29,"verse":45,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" and we bear your name."},{"kind":"text","text":" Don’t leave us!"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Is 59:1","book":"Isa","chapter":59,"verse":1},{"label":"Ex 29:45","book":"Exo","chapter":29,"verse":45}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:14:10","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"This is what the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" says concerning these people:"},{"kind":"text","text":" Truly they love to wander; "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 5:31","book":"Jer","chapter":5,"verse":31,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Am 8:12","book":"Amo","chapter":8,"verse":12,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" they never rest their feet."},{"kind":"text","text":" So the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" does not accept them."},{"kind":"text","text":" Now he will remember their iniquity"},{"kind":"text","text":" and punish their sins. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Hs 8:13","book":"Hos","chapter":8,"verse":13,"letter":"a"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jr 5:31","book":"Jer","chapter":5,"verse":31},{"label":"Am 8:12","book":"Amo","chapter":8,"verse":12},{"label":"Hs 8:13","book":"Hos","chapter":8,"verse":13}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:14:11","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Then the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" said to me, “Do not pray for the well-being of these people. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 7:16","book":"Jer","chapter":7,"verse":16,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 11:14","book":"Jer","chapter":11,"verse":14,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 15:1","book":"Jer","chapter":15,"verse":1,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jr 7:16","book":"Jer","chapter":7,"verse":16},{"label":"Jr 11:14","book":"Jer","chapter":11,"verse":14},{"label":"Jr 15:1","book":"Jer","chapter":15,"verse":1}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:14:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"If they fast, I will not hear their cry of despair. If they offer burnt offering and grain offering, I will not accept them. Rather, I will finish them off by sword, famine, and plague.” "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 5:12","book":"Jer","chapter":5,"verse":12,"letter":"a"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jr 5:12","book":"Jer","chapter":5,"verse":12}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:14:13","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"And I replied, “Oh no, Lord "},{"kind":"text","text":"God","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":"! The prophets are telling them, ‘You won’t see sword or suffer famine. I will certainly give you lasting peace in this place.’” "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 4:10","book":"Jer","chapter":4,"verse":10,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 6:13–14","book":"Jer","chapter":6,"verse":13,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 8:10–12","book":"Jer","chapter":8,"verse":10,"letter":"c"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jr 4:10","book":"Jer","chapter":4,"verse":10},{"label":"Jr 6:13–14","book":"Jer","chapter":6,"verse":13},{"label":"Jr 8:10–12","book":"Jer","chapter":8,"verse":10}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:14:14","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" said to me, “These prophets are prophesying a lie in my name. I did not send them, nor did I command them or speak to them. They are prophesying to you a false vision, worthless divination, the deceit "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 119:118","book":"Psa","chapter":119,"verse":118,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 8:5","book":"Jer","chapter":8,"verse":5,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 23:26","book":"Jer","chapter":23,"verse":26,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" of their own minds. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 5:31","book":"Jer","chapter":5,"verse":31,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 20:6","book":"Jer","chapter":20,"verse":6,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 23:25–26","book":"Jer","chapter":23,"verse":25,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 23:32","book":"Jer","chapter":23,"verse":32,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 27:10","book":"Jer","chapter":27,"verse":10,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 27:14","book":"Jer","chapter":27,"verse":14,"letter":"i"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 29:9","book":"Jer","chapter":29,"verse":9,"letter":"j"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 29:21","book":"Jer","chapter":29,"verse":21,"letter":"k"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 29:31","book":"Jer","chapter":29,"verse":31,"letter":"l"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ps 119:118","book":"Psa","chapter":119,"verse":118},{"label":"Jr 8:5","book":"Jer","chapter":8,"verse":5},{"label":"Jr 23:26","book":"Jer","chapter":23,"verse":26},{"label":"Jr 5:31","book":"Jer","chapter":5,"verse":31},{"label":"Jr 20:6","book":"Jer","chapter":20,"verse":6},{"label":"Jr 23:25–26","book":"Jer","chapter":23,"verse":25},{"label":"Jr 23:32","book":"Jer","chapter":23,"verse":32},{"label":"Jr 27:10","book":"Jer","chapter":27,"verse":10},{"label":"Jr 27:14","book":"Jer","chapter":27,"verse":14},{"label":"Jr 29:9","book":"Jer","chapter":29,"verse":9},{"label":"Jr 29:21","book":"Jer","chapter":29,"verse":21},{"label":"Jr 29:31","book":"Jer","chapter":29,"verse":31}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:14:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“Therefore, this is what the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" says concerning the prophets who prophesy in my name, though I did not send them, and who say, ‘There will never be sword or famine in this land.’ By sword and famine these prophets will meet their end. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:14:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The people they are prophesying to will be thrown into the streets of Jerusalem because of the famine and the sword. There will be no one to bury them "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 7:33","book":"Jer","chapter":7,"verse":33,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 9:22","book":"Jer","chapter":9,"verse":22,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" —they, their wives, their sons, and their daughters. I will pour out their own evil on them.”"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jr 7:33","book":"Jer","chapter":7,"verse":33},{"label":"Jr 9:22","book":"Jer","chapter":9,"verse":22}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:14:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"You are to speak this word to them:"},{"kind":"text","text":" Let my eyes overflow with tears;"},{"kind":"text","text":" day and night may they not stop, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 9:1","book":"Jer","chapter":9,"verse":1,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 9:10","book":"Jer","chapter":9,"verse":10,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 13:17","book":"Jer","chapter":13,"verse":17,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" for my dearest people "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit for the virgin daughter of my people"},{"kind":"text","text":" have been destroyed by a crushing blow, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 4:6","book":"Jer","chapter":4,"verse":6,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 6:1","book":"Jer","chapter":6,"verse":1,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" an extremely severe wound. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 10:19","book":"Jer","chapter":10,"verse":19,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 30:12","book":"Jer","chapter":30,"verse":12,"letter":"b"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jr 9:1","book":"Jer","chapter":9,"verse":1},{"label":"Jr 9:10","book":"Jer","chapter":9,"verse":10},{"label":"Jr 13:17","book":"Jer","chapter":13,"verse":17},{"label":"Jr 4:6","book":"Jer","chapter":4,"verse":6},{"label":"Jr 6:1","book":"Jer","chapter":6,"verse":1},{"label":"Jr 10:19","book":"Jer","chapter":10,"verse":19},{"label":"Jr 30:12","book":"Jer","chapter":30,"verse":12}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit for the virgin daughter of my people"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:14:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"If I go out to the field,"},{"kind":"text","text":" look —those slain by the sword!"},{"kind":"text","text":" If I enter the city,"},{"kind":"text","text":" look —those ill "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 29:22","book":"Deu","chapter":29,"verse":22,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" from famine!"},{"kind":"text","text":" For both prophet and priest"},{"kind":"text","text":" travel to a land they do not know."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Dt 29:22","book":"Deu","chapter":29,"verse":22}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:14:19","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Have you completely rejected Judah?"},{"kind":"text","text":" Do you detest "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 26:11","book":"Lev","chapter":26,"verse":11,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 26:30","book":"Lev","chapter":26,"verse":30,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 26:43","book":"Lev","chapter":26,"verse":43,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" Zion?"},{"kind":"text","text":" Why do you strike us"},{"kind":"text","text":" with no hope of healing for us?"},{"kind":"text","text":" We hoped for peace,"},{"kind":"text","text":" but there was nothing good;"},{"kind":"text","text":" for a time of healing,"},{"kind":"text","text":" but there was only terror. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 8:15","book":"Jer","chapter":8,"verse":15,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 33:9","book":"Jer","chapter":33,"verse":9,"letter":"b"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lv 26:11","book":"Lev","chapter":26,"verse":11},{"label":"Lv 26:30","book":"Lev","chapter":26,"verse":30},{"label":"Lv 26:43","book":"Lev","chapter":26,"verse":43},{"label":"Jr 8:15","book":"Jer","chapter":8,"verse":15},{"label":"Jr 33:9","book":"Jer","chapter":33,"verse":9}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:14:20","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"We acknowledge our wickedness, "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"text","text":" the iniquity of our ancestors; "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 3:25","book":"Jer","chapter":3,"verse":25,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 11:10","book":"Jer","chapter":11,"verse":10,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 16:12–13","book":"Jer","chapter":16,"verse":12,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" indeed, we have sinned against you."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jr 3:25","book":"Jer","chapter":3,"verse":25},{"label":"Jr 11:10","book":"Jer","chapter":11,"verse":10},{"label":"Jr 16:12–13","book":"Jer","chapter":16,"verse":12}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:14:21","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For your name’s sake, don’t despise us."},{"kind":"text","text":" Don’t disdain your glorious throne. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 32:19","book":"Deu","chapter":32,"verse":19,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 15:6","book":"Jer","chapter":15,"verse":6,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 17:12","book":"Jer","chapter":17,"verse":12,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" Remember your covenant "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 26:44","book":"Lev","chapter":26,"verse":44,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jdg 2:1","book":"Jdg","chapter":2,"verse":1,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 33:8","book":"Isa","chapter":33,"verse":8,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" with us;"},{"kind":"text","text":" do not break it."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Dt 32:19","book":"Deu","chapter":32,"verse":19},{"label":"Jr 15:6","book":"Jer","chapter":15,"verse":6},{"label":"Jr 17:12","book":"Jer","chapter":17,"verse":12},{"label":"Lv 26:44","book":"Lev","chapter":26,"verse":44},{"label":"Jdg 2:1","book":"Jdg","chapter":2,"verse":1},{"label":"Is 33:8","book":"Isa","chapter":33,"verse":8}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Jer:14:22","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Can any of the worthless idols of the nations "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 8:19","book":"Jer","chapter":8,"verse":19,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 10:8","book":"Jer","chapter":10,"verse":8,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 10:15","book":"Jer","chapter":10,"verse":15,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 16:19","book":"Jer","chapter":16,"verse":19,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" bring rain?"},{"kind":"text","text":" Or can the skies alone give showers?"},{"kind":"text","text":" Are you not the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" our God?"},{"kind":"text","text":" We therefore put our hope in you, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 8:17","book":"Isa","chapter":8,"verse":17,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 25:9","book":"Isa","chapter":25,"verse":9,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" for you have done all these things."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jr 8:19","book":"Jer","chapter":8,"verse":19},{"label":"Jr 10:8","book":"Jer","chapter":10,"verse":8},{"label":"Jr 10:15","book":"Jer","chapter":10,"verse":15},{"label":"Jr 16:19","book":"Jer","chapter":16,"verse":19},{"label":"Is 8:17","book":"Isa","chapter":8,"verse":17},{"label":"Is 25:9","book":"Isa","chapter":25,"verse":9}],"footnotes":[]}]},"cachedAt":1783279561768}